graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kueue -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+<br/>Required]
    Kueue -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Optional]
    Kueue -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional]
    Kueue -.->|node provisioning| Autoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler<br/>with ProvisioningRequest API<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Kueue -->|queues| KubeFlowTraining[KubeFlow Training Operator<br/>PyTorchJob, TFJob, MPIJob]
    Kueue -->|queues| RayOp[Ray Operator<br/>RayJob, RayCluster]
    Kueue -->|queues| JobSetOp[JobSet Operator<br/>JobSet]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI for queue mgmt| Kueue
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|job submission| Kueue

    %% External Services (Multi-cluster)
    Kueue -.->|multi-cluster| RemoteClusters[Remote Kubernetes Clusters<br/>MultiKueue<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Job Types (CRDs watched)
    Kueue -->|manages| BatchJob[Batch Job<br/>batch/v1]
    Kueue -->|manages| PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    Kueue -->|manages| TFJob[TFJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    Kueue -->|manages| MPIJob[MPIJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    Kueue -->|manages| RayJob[RayJob<br/>ray.io/v1]
    Kueue -->|manages| RayCluster[RayCluster<br/>ray.io/v1]
    Kueue -->|manages| JobSet[JobSet<br/>jobset.x-k8s.io/v1alpha2]

    %% Kueue CRDs
    Kueue -->|defines| Workload[Workload CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]
    Kueue -->|defines| ClusterQueue[ClusterQueue CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]
    Kueue -->|defines| LocalQueue[LocalQueue CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]
    Kueue -->|defines| ResourceFlavor[ResourceFlavor CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]

